  <subsection xml:id="UNIQUE-ID-000671">
    <title>Summary</title>
    <p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>Primitive values and reference values can be compared using relational operators (i.e., <c>==</c> and <c>!=</c>) in Java.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>Arithmetic expression values can be compared using relational operators (i.e., <c>&lt;</c>, <c>&gt;</c>, <c>&lt;=</c>, <c>&gt;=</c>) in Java.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>An expression involving relational operators evaluates to a <c>boolean</c> value of <c>true</c> or <c>false</c>.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </subsection>
